{"word":"ξενιτεύω","slug":"ξενιτεύω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ξενιτεύω</b></el> <el>(ξενῑτεύω,) ( φυτ. <el>-σω</el>) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><el>ξένος</el>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>to live abroad</i>, <b><a href='S:Lucian'>Luc.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><a href='S:Deponent Verb, i.e. a Verb of Middle or Passive form with Active sense'>Dep.</a> <el>ξενιτεύομαι</el>, <i>to be in foreign service</i>, <b><a href='S:Isocrates'>Isocr.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}